<p align="left"><b><font face="Arial" color="#000086" size="3">Positions available immediately in Johannesburg</font></b></p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p align="left"><a href="#Mechanical Sales"><b><font face="Arial" size="3">Mechanical
    Sales</font></b></a></li>
  <li>
    <p align="left"><b><a href="#Part time marketing and sales post.  Suited to ex teacher with degree."><font face="Arial" size="3">Marketing
and Sales&nbsp;</font></a></b></li>
</ul>
<p align="left"><font color="#000086" face="Arial" size="4"><strong><a name="Mechanical Sales">Mechanical
Sales</a></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
<p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="3">Challenging and interesting position
for enthusiast with mechanical engineering background.&nbsp; Join our strong,
goal oriented team developing new markets locally and abroad, who take pride in
solving the wear problems of our customers, saving them time and money.</font></p>
<ul>
  <li><font face="Arial" size="3">technical environment</font></li>
  <li><font face="Arial" size="3">selling engineering polymers</font></li>
  <li><font face="Arial" size="3">to a well established market</font></li>
  <li><font face="Arial" size="3">possible opportunities abroad<br>
    </font></li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
  <p><font face="Arial" size="3" color="#000086"><b>Requirements</b></font></p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
  <li><font color="#400040" face="Arial" size="3">sound technical and mechanical
    background</font></li>
  <li><font color="#400040" face="Arial" size="3">with creativity and flair</font></li>
  <li><font color="#400040" face="Arial" size="3">to help grow our customer base
    into the new millenium</font></li>
  <li><font color="#400040" face="Arial" size="3">self starter, independent,
    self motivated</font></li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
  <p><b><font face="Arial" size="3" color="#000086">Benefits</font></b></p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
  <li><font color="#400040" face="Arial" size="3">partnership scheme</font></li>
  <li><font color="#400040" face="Arial" size="3">stable company</font></li>
  <li><font color="#400040" face="Arial" size="3">challenging and stimulating
    work</font></li>
  <li><font color="#400040" face="Arial" size="3">help break into world markets</font></li>
  <li><font color="#400040" face="Arial" size="3">meet original equipment
    manufacturers around the world</font></li>
  <li><font color="#400040" face="Arial" size="3">pension, medical aid, 13th
    cheque</font></li>
</ul>
<p><font face="Arial" size="3">&nbsp;</font></p>

<p align="left"><b><font face="Arial" size="3" color="#000086"><a name="Part time marketing and sales post.  Suited to ex teacher with degree.">Part time marketing
and sales post.&nbsp; Suited to ex teacher with degree.</a></font></b></p>

<blockquote>

  <p><font face="Arial" color="#000086" size="3"><b>Requirements</b></font></p>

</blockquote>

<ul>
  <li><font face="Arial" color="#400040">Good English writing skills</font></li>
  <li><font face="Arial" color="#400040">Portuguese and/or Spanish recommended
    but not essential</font></li>
  <li><font face="Arial" color="#400040">Willingness to learn basic computer
    literacy, e-mail and web usage</font></li>
  <li><font face="Arial" color="#400040">Good typing skills</font></li>
</ul>

<blockquote>

<p><font face="Arial" color="#000086" size="3"><b>Responsibilities</b></font></p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
  <li><font face="Arial" size="3">Customer liaison in foreign markets</font></li>
  <li><font face="Arial" size="3">Planning and writing of company literature and
    direct mailing campaigns</font></li>
  <li><font face="Arial" size="3">e-mail follow up</font></li>
</ul>
